*'''Passatismo'''
*'''Passéism'''
*'''Passéist'''

===Origin===
*From ''passato'' meaning [[past]]. Derogatory neologism created by the Italian Futurists, defined below by Marinetti.

===Meaning===
# "state of mind which is passive, traditional, professional, pessimistic, pacifist, nostalgic, decorative and aesthetic."